    <item>
      <title>印度预测季风将高于正常水平以促进经济增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/india-predicts-above-normal-monsoon-in-boost-to-economic-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度预计今年的季风将高于正常水平，人们乐观地认为，充足的降雨将刺激农作物产量和经济增长，并促使政府放松对小麦、大米和食糖出口的限制。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/india-predicts-above-normal-monsoon-in-boost-to-economic-growth</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 09:16:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据当地媒体报道，越南国家银行本周将恢复黄金拍卖</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/vietnam-s-state-bank-to-resume-gold-auctions-this-week-media</link>
      <description><![CDATA[《An Ninh Thu Do》报纸在其网站上援引越南国家银行的信息报道称，越南国家银行计划最早于 4 月 17 日进行 11 年来的首次金条拍卖。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/vietnam-s-state-bank-to-resume-gold-auctions-this-week-media</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 09:00:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于进口费用较低，印度 3 月份贸易逆差收窄至 11 个月低点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/india-march-trade-gap-narrows-to-11-month-low-on-low-import-bill</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于印度控制进口开支以及全球需求复苏提振出口，印度 3 月份贸易逆差收窄至 11 个月低点。]]></description>
