      <title>万科准备180亿美元资产作为新贷款的抵押品</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/vanke-readies-18-billion-of-assets-as-collateral-for-new-loans</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，中国政府支持的开发商万科集团正在准备总额约1300亿元人民币（合180亿美元）的资产包，作为寻求新银行贷款的抵押品。此事说。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/vanke-readies-18-billion-of-assets-as-collateral-for-new-loans</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 08:23:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
